sequenceDiagram
    participant Investor
    participant DALP as DALP Platform
    participant OID as OnchainID
    participant Policy as SMART Policy Engine
    participant Chain as EVM Network

    Investor->>DALP: Request Transfer
    DALP->>OID: Verify Sender Identity
    OID-->>DALP: Claims: KYC, AML, Country
    DALP->>OID: Verify Receiver Identity
    OID-->>DALP: Claims: Accreditation, Eligibility
    DALP->>Policy: Evaluate Transfer Rules
    Note over Policy: Country Allow/Block List<br/>Investor Count Limit<br/>Supply Cap Check<br/>Time Lock Validation
    Policy-->>DALP: Compliant: Yes/No
    alt Transfer Approved
        DALP->>Chain: Execute Transfer
        Chain-->>DALP: Transaction Confirmed
        DALP-->>Investor: Transfer Complete
    else Transfer Rejected
        DALP-->>Investor: Rejection with Reason
    end
